%% v1.5 - Added Backend LLM API calls for Docs & Obligations
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant App as Android App
    participant Firestore as Firestore DB
    participant BackendLLMAPI as Backend LLM API (Cloud Func)
    participant LLM as LLM Service (Gemini)
    participant CloudFuncOrch as Metadata Orchestrator (Cloud Func)
    participant Email as Email Service (Brevo)

    User->>App: Start App Session
    App->>Firestore: Store APP_SESSION_START Event (+deviceInfo)
    App->>CloudFuncOrch: Trigger Metadata Event (processEvent)

    User->>App: Navigate to Screen (e.g., Document Upload)
    App->>Firestore: Store SCREEN_VISIT Event (startTime)
    App->>CloudFuncOrch: Trigger Metadata Event

    User->>App: Upload Document (e.g., Bank Statement PDF)
    App->>Firestore: Store DOCUMENT_EVENT (UPLOAD_STARTED)
    App->>CloudFuncOrch: Trigger Metadata Event
    App->>BackendLLMAPI: Trigger processDocument (AppID, DocID, PDF Content)
    Note right of App: UI Shows Spinner for Bank Stmt

    BackendLLMAPI->>+LLM: Send PDF data + prompt for extraction
    LLM-->>-BackendLLMAPI: Return Structured JSON Data
    BackendLLMAPI->>Firestore: Update documents/{docId} (extractedData, status=PROCESSED)
    Note left of BackendLLMAPI: Asynchronous Response

    %% User might continue uploading other documents in parallel...

    User->>App: Navigate to Bureau Confirmation Screen (Conditional)
    App->>Firestore: Store SCREEN_VISIT Event (endTime, duration) for Doc Upload
    App->>Firestore: Store SCREEN_VISIT Event (startTime) for Bureau Confirm
    App->>CloudFuncOrch: Trigger Metadata Events

    User->>App: Input EMIs & Comments, Submit Bureau Confirmation
    App->>Firestore: Store OBLIGATION_REFINEMENT data (user input)
    App->>Firestore: Store OBLIGATION_REFINEMENT_SUBMITTED Event
    App->>CloudFuncOrch: Trigger Metadata Event
    App->>BackendLLMAPI: Trigger recalculateObligation (AppID, RefinementID)

    BackendLLMAPI->>Firestore: Read Obligation Input Data
    BackendLLMAPI->>+LLM: Send Tradeline/User Data + prompt
    LLM-->>-BackendLLMAPI: Return Recalculated Obligation JSON
    BackendLLMAPI->>Firestore: Update obligationRefinement/{id} (LLM results)
    Note left of BackendLLMAPI: Asynchronous Response

    %% User might navigate away while LLM processing happens...

    User->>App: Put App in Background
    App->>Firestore: Store APP_BACKGROUNDED Event
    App->>CloudFuncOrch: Trigger processEvent
    CloudFuncOrch->>Firestore: Write to backgrounded_apps

    %% Drop-off Check (Scheduled)
    activate CloudFuncOrch
    CloudFuncOrch->>Firestore: Query backgrounded_apps
    CloudFuncOrch->>Firestore: Query applications (status)
    CloudFuncOrch->>Firestore: Query metadata (recent events)

    alt Drop-off Confirmed
        CloudFuncOrch->>Firestore: Update App Status to DROPPED_OFF
        CloudFuncOrch->>Firestore: Fetch App Data & Metadata
        CloudFuncOrch->>+LLM: Send Drop-off Analysis Request
        LLM-->>-CloudFuncOrch: Return Drop-off Analysis
        CloudFuncOrch->>+Email: Send Drop-off Summary Alert
        Email-->>-CloudFuncOrch: Email Sent Confirmation
    end
    deactivate CloudFuncOrch

    alt User Returns Within Timeout
        User->>App: Bring App to Foreground
        App->>Firestore: Store APP_FOREGROUNDED Event
        App->>CloudFuncOrch: Trigger processEvent
        CloudFuncOrch->>Firestore: Delete from backgrounded_apps
    end

    Note over User,Email: End of Example Flow